<http://model.geneontology.org/ev_w_id_R-HSA-9934751_RO_0002234_R-HSA-191697_R-HSA-9934751_Reactome_R-HSA-9766229_R-HSA-9934751_enabled_by_UniProt_P12931_R-HSA-9934751_controller>
